<paragraph blockId="4.[111,648,882,1256]" box="[113,213,882,908]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">REMARKS</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[111,648,882,1256]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">
According to 
<bibRefCitation author="QUATTROCCHI U." box="[255,463,913,939]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" pagination="1 - 4" refId="ref13674" refString="QUATTROCCHI U. 2000. - CRC World Dictionary of Plant Names. CRC Press, Boca Raton, vols 1 - 4." type="book chapter" year="2000">Quattrocchi (2000)</bibRefCitation>
the generic name is from the Greek word “ 
<emphasis box="[393,462,945,971]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">geisson</emphasis>
” meaning a tile, and refers to the overlapping winged seeds in the dehiscent fruits. 
<bibRefCitation author="POST T. VON &amp; KUNTZE O." box="[299,547,1008,1034]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" refId="ref13643" refString="POST T. VON &amp; KUNTZE O. 1903. - Lexicon Generum Phanerogamarum. Deutsche Verlag-Anstalt, Stuttgart, 714 p. (dated 1904, published 1903)." type="book" year="1903">Post &amp; Kuntze (1903)</bibRefCitation>
gave the name as “ 
<emphasis box="[220,288,1040,1066]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">Gissois</emphasis>
Lab.”, but their alteration of the spelling was not adopted and is not included in indices such as 
<taxonomicName authority="Nominum Genericorum" authorityName="Nominum Genericorum" box="[266,565,1104,1130]" class="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" family="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" genus="Index" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[266,565,1104,1130]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">Index Nominum Genericorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(http:// ravenel.si.edu/notany/ing/ingForm.cfm, consulted 
<date box="[112,273,1167,1193]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" value="2006-03-30">30 March 2006</date>
) or 
<taxonomicName authority="Kewensis" authorityName="Kewensis" box="[314,462,1167,1193]" class="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" family="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" genus="Index" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[314,462,1167,1193]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="315">Index Kewensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see International Plant Names 
<taxonomicName box="[258,322,1199,1225]" class="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" family="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" genus="Index" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" pageId="4" pageNumber="326" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">Index</taxonomicName>
, website http://www.ipni.org, consulted 
<date box="[224,398,1230,1256]" pageId="4" pageNumber="315" value="2006-03-30">30 March 2006</date>
).
</paragraph>
